  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ includes a powerful Business Intelligence (BI) Suite, provided through integration with Looker. This tool offers a set of visual dashboards covering key performance indicators (KPIs) essential for running a retail repair business. These reports allow you to quickly view important aspects of your business, such as sales trends, inventory levels, and repair progress, helping you make more informed decisions.</p><p>Our Business Intelligence (BI) Dashboards are available to Admin users on our Advanced and Professional plans. Users on the <strong>Advanced Plan</strong> can view a wide range of pre-built reports and dashboards, giving them access to critical insights about their business. However, they are limited to viewing these pre-made reports and cannot create new ones. <strong>Professional Plan</strong> users can view pre-built reports and build custom reports. This allows them to tailor reports to their specific needs and gain deeper insights from their data.</p><p>Below are solutions to common issues you may encounter when accessing Business Intelligence (BI) features.</p><h3 id=\"BusinessIntelligence-Troubleshooting-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2731114524\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Intelligence (BI) Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936621637\" rel=\"nofollow\">Analytics Dashboards - Explore and Download Data</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937866763/Reporting+Resources+with+Video\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937866763\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reporting Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937014903/Clearing+Your+Cache+in+Chrome+Browser\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937014903\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Clearing Your Cache in Chrome Browser</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Instructional - 0091cd.png\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936392337/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"BusinessIntelligence-Troubleshooting-Youarenotauthenticatedtoviewthispage.401\">You are not authenticated to view this page. 401</h2><p>This error occurs because your browser is blocking third-party cookies. To resolve this, go to your browser's settings and navigate to the <strong>Advanced</strong> section. Find the <strong>Content</strong> or <strong>Privacy</strong> settings and locate the <strong>Cookies</strong> option. Ensure that <strong>&quot;Block third-party cookies&quot;</strong> is not checked.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936392337/image-20230607-172937.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936392337/image-20230607-172950.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
